<div class='title-box'>
<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

</div>
<div class='content-box'>
<div id="TOC"><ol>
  <li>
    <a href="#summary">Summary</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="#information-we-collect-and-retain">Information we collect and retain</a>
